{"tid":104363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"安永員工排隊1小時𢭃百元開工利是  德勤派20元","createTime":"2017-02-02T05:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T06:57:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99db4b04aa74922fd6512373c575a83893d1f942","tid":104363,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:09:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170202/19915356\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170202%2F19915356&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=99f91bbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170202%2F19915356&h=0b074e78\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170202/19915356</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170202/large/02la5p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170202%2Flarge%2F02la5p3.jpg&h=d476491b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n■安永昨有大批員工排隊向管理層拜年。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一連數天農曆年假結束，打工仔當然期望收到大大封開工利是，但本港經濟持續低迷，大部份企業開工利是金額「冰封」，由20元至2,000元不等，其中以中信銀行最闊綽，向員工派發2,000元大利是；13年來首次錄得虧損的海洋公園，亦維持派發1,200元利是。四大會計師樓之一的安永（EY），昨日有管理層派發100元開工利是，吸引大批員工排隊拜年，輪候逾一小時後始獲取利是。 <br />\n<br />\n安永昨有管理層派100元的開工利是，吸引大批員工由下午2時半「恭候」拜年，排隊逾一小時終獲取利是，有員工說：「排吓冇所謂嘅，都係想Hea吓箒！」另外一間會計師樓德勤則派20元開工利是。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3a83801fdd867857d11da0fafcf6210202d324","tid":104363,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:13:23.000Z","msg":"皇恩浩蕩"},{"pid":"557f7d0a4fbeb1729514c6d41994194283f72a08","tid":104363,"uid":10340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"又話逼科好忙，排成個鍾先一舊水，唔使做咁！<br />\nPs:開工利是都係100，hr 自動送上黎！"},{"pid":"55dcfbfbdbaff9cac8250f6391fe9bc42a79b110","tid":104363,"uid":76776,"like":0